# Triangle without normal vectors — uses v/vt face format (no normal index).
# The parser expects v/vt/vn and panics when the normal index token is missing.
# This file documents the assumption: all OBJ files must include vertex normals.
v  0.0  0.0  0.0
v  1.0  0.0  0.0
v  0.5  1.0  0.0
vt 0.0  0.0
vt 1.0  0.0
vt 0.5  1.0
f  1/1 2/2 3/3
